snippet.title: TETRIS 99 - Big Block DLC (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Two new offline modes have landed in TETRIS 99's Big Block DLC! Battle against 98 bots in CPU Battle, or go for the most lines and the highest score in Marathon!

An additional offline multiplayer mode will also arrive later this year as part of the Big Block DLC, with more details to follow at a later date.

Buy now: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/TETRIS-99-1505396.html?utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=Tetris99%7CDLCAnnouncement%7Co2LPV%7Cw19#Downloadable_content
